# MantleJS

A KubeJS addon for [Mantle](https://curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/mantle) things.

## Current contents

- Custom Mantle books

## Bug report

Report bugs on [GitHub](https://github.com/Pelemenguin/Mantle).

## Tutorials

See [GitHub](https://github.com/Pelemenguin/MantleJS/blob/docs/.tutorial/tutorial/toc.md).

An example to create a Mantle book.

```javascript
// Script type: STARTUP
MantleJSEvents.bookRegistry(event => {
    // Create the book here
    event.create("test")
        // Specify the book repository
        .addBookRepository("kubejs:book/test");
});
StartupEvents.registry('item', event => {
    // Create a book item
    event.create("test_book", "mantle:book")
        // Set the book data
        .setBookData("test");
});
```
